Over time I have purchased maybe 120+ icon packs on Play Store, and one of the most important features I look for (especially in packs with all uniform-shaped icons) is the masking for un‚Äêthemed icons. I have maaany apps, and not all will be covered. Normally these "transparent style" packs have terrible masking, but this pack's is superb. Maintaining the 'black‚Äîwhite' theme by removing all color from the original app icon, and having it sized perfectly in center. Very pleased with this pack.

I love the icons but since latest updates, all my packs by this dev seem to have lost their search functionality. Nothing shows up when I search. This means that the 30 or so icons I have which actually are themed but don't apply automatically cannot now be applied manually because searching for them doesn't work. I have several Sky apps that don't apply, the NatWest app, my train app... What does the dev expect us to do? Am I expected to literally scroll through the thousands of icons to find these? Something has gone wrong with search & it's making all of these packs useless to me!
